# Design System

A dark navy + electric teal palette for an IT / infrastructure / DevOps
professional brand. All values are defined as CSS custom properties in
`assets/css/tokens.css` — reference tokens, never hard-coded values.

## Typography
- **Display font:** `'Cabinet Grotesk'` (Fontshare) — headings `h1`–`h3`.
- **Body font:** `'Satoshi'` (Fontshare) — body text, nav, buttons.
- Load fonts via the Fontshare CDN:
  `https://api.fontshare.com/v2/css?f[]=cabinet-grotesk@...&f[]=satoshi@...&display=swap`.
- Type scale uses `clamp()` custom properties `--text-xs` … `--text-hero`.
- **Minimum text size: 12px** (`--text-xs` floor). Body copy at `--text-base`
  (16px minimum).
- Display font only used at `--text-xl` (24px) and above.

## Color
- Tokens: `--color-bg`, `--color-surface`, `--color-text`, `--color-primary`
  (teal accent), `--color-text-muted`, plus supporting surface/border tokens.
- Themes via `[data-theme="dark"]` and `[data-theme="light"]`.
- System default via `prefers-color-scheme`.
- Manual toggle via a sun/moon button in the header (`[data-theme-toggle]`).
- **Dark mode is the default aesthetic.**

## Spacing
- 4px base unit. Tokens `--space-1` (4px) … `--space-32` (128px).

## Radius
- `--radius-sm` (6px), `--radius-md` (8px), `--radius-lg` (12px),
  `--radius-xl` (16px), `--radius-full` (9999px).

## Shadows
- Tone-matched to dark surfaces using `oklch()` with alpha:
  `--shadow-sm`, `--shadow-md`, `--shadow-lg`, `--shadow-focus`.

## Transitions
- `--transition-interactive: 180ms cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)`.
- `--transition-slow` for reveal animations.

## Content widths
- `--content-narrow: 640px`, `--content-default: 960px`,
  `--content-wide: 1200px`.

## Design DON'Ts
- No emoji as design elements.
- No gradient buttons.
- No icon-in-colored-circle patterns.
- No inline styles.
